otherCommentsOrNotes: Interesting here that the supervisor integrates opinion based questions into the case. This was designed to elicit the opinions of the CHWs and try invoke rich discussions as well as more detailed opinions, as well as spark discussion between CHWs and encourage different opinions/answers. With the previous knowledge based questions there was less opportunity for independant thought and for CHWs to consider the broader issues at play which affect access to care and quality of healthcare delivery.
